videos.headline: BC's Flowers goes up and hauls in TD
videos.description: Boston College wide receiver Zay Flowers elevates and grabs the 33-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (BC's Flowers goes up and hauls in TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Willis finds wide-open Grimsley for the Hokies' TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Ryan Willis links up with a wide-open Hezekiah Grimsley for the long 55-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Willis finds wide-open Grimsley for the Hokies’ TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Willis fires a pass to Robinson for the Virginia Tech TD
videos.description: Ryan Willis threads the needle and finds Tayvion Robinson who lunges in for the Virginia Tech touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Willis fires a pass to Robinson for the Virginia Tech TD) 2019/08/31

videos.headline: Dillon bounces off defender then scores a BC TD
videos.description: Boston College RB AJ Dillon goes right then turns back left and walks into the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dillon bounces off defender then scores a BC TD) 2019/08/31
